code: /**  * Creates a Command to test execution.  */ protected abstract Command newCommand().

comment: /**  * Runs the command with the given args.  *  * Output can be found in {@link #terminal}.  * The command created can be found in {@link #command}.  */
code: /**  * Runs the command with the given args.  *  * Output can be found in {@link #terminal}.  * The command created can be found in {@link #command}.  */ public String execute(String... args) throws Exception {     command = newCommand().     command.mainWithoutErrorHandling(args, terminal).     return terminal.getOutput(). }
